cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about object detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.NE) and end-to-end training (cs.LG) for the task. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of attention mechanisms (cs.AI) and achieving state-of-the-art results on benchmark datasets (cs.MM).
